{"case_id": "STD_007", "input": {"query": "ZBAA现在满足什么进近标准", "role": "pilot", "metar": "METAR ZBAA 0900Z 22018KT 1500 OVC008 12/11 Q1005"}, "output": "当前天气条件：能见度1.5km，云底高800ft OVC。根据ICAO Annex 3标准，这属于LIFR（低仪表飞行规则）条件。\n\n进近标准分析：\n1. ILS CAT I：DH 200ft，云底高800ft满足要求，但能见度1.5km低于标准（通常要求RVR 550m或能见度800m以上）。需要确认具体RVR要求。\n2. ILS CAT II：DH 100ft，云底高满足，但能见度不足。\n3. ILS CAT III：DH 0ft，云底高满足，能见度不足。\n4. VOR进近：MDA 500ft，云底高800ft满足，能见度1.5km可能满足非精密进近要求。\n\n建议使用ILS CAT I进近，但需要确认RVR设备读数。如果能见度稳定在1.5km，可以执行CAT I进近。需要确认跑道方向以计算侧风分量，当前风向220度18节。", "latency_ms": 15697, "tokens": null, "provider": "deepseek", "error": null, "error_type": null, "score": {"task_completed": true, "key_info_hit_rate": 0.25, "is_template": false, "overall_score": 0.775, "details": {"task_check": {"passed": true, "confidence": 0.9, "reason": "检测到3个结论模式"}, "key_info": {"hit_rate": 0.25, "hits": 1, "total": 4, "missed": ["能见度低", "云底高低", "需要仪表进近"]}, "template_check": {"is_template": false, "score": 0.0, "reasons": []}, "safety_check": {"passed": true, "missed_criticals": []}}}, "judge": null, "timestamp": "2026-04-16T02:35:34.568801"}
