{"case_id": "STD_049", "input": {"query": "ZSSS天气怎么样（雷暴天气）", "role": "pilot", "metar": "METAR ZSSS 1200Z 27025G40KT 0800 +TSRA BKN010CB 18/17 Q0998"}, "output": "ZSSS天气严重恶化。能见度<1km，云底高1000ft，飞行规则LIFR。270度风25节阵风40节，强雷暴伴雨。这是危险天气，不适合起降。雷暴区存在严重颠簸、风切变和强降水风险。建议等待天气好转或备降。", "latency_ms": 18738, "tokens": null, "provider": "deepseek", "error": null, "error_type": null, "score": {"task_completed": true, "key_info_hit_rate": 0.25, "is_template": false, "overall_score": 0.775, "details": {"task_check": {"passed": true, "confidence": 0.9, "reason": "检测到3个结论模式"}, "key_info": {"hit_rate": 0.25, "hits": 1, "total": 4, "missed": ["强阵风", "CRITICAL", "不适合进近"]}, "template_check": {"is_template": false, "score": 0.0, "reasons": []}, "safety_check": {"passed": true, "missed_criticals": []}}}, "judge": null, "timestamp": "2026-04-16T02:46:43.333528"}
